com.rs.seagull.emulator.api

Interface StartupInformation

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    StartupInformation.Ibm3270, StartupInformation.Ibm5250

    public interface StartupInformation
    This interface describes the startup information for a host session. There are implementations for IBM 3270 and IBM 5250.
    Version:
    $Id: CJL2CodeTemplates.xml,v 1.2 2011/02/16 16:13:58 MRomijn Exp $
    Author:
    mromijn

    • Method Detail

      • getEmulator

        String getEmulator()
        Get the type of emulator for which this is the startup information. This can be String Ibm3270, in case this startup information is an instance of StartupInformation.Ibm3270. This can be String Ibm5250, in case this startup information is an instance of StartupInformation.Ibm5250.
        Returns:
        the type of emulator for which this is the startup information
